# Fit Elite PWA — Antigravity Test Suite
# Sync Layer + iOS Safari Compatibility
# Version: 1.0 | Phase 5

---

## CONTEXT

You are testing **Fit Elite** — a Progressive Web App (PWA) workout tracker.
Stack: Vanilla JS, Web Components, IndexedDB, Express/Node.js, Supabase.

The app is **local-first**: IndexedDB is the single source of truth.
Supabase sync happens in the background via an **Outbox Pattern**.

Base URL: http://localhost:3000
Supabase project: https://hkpuxvqzhcwgtbyjyinx.supabase.co

---

## ARCHITECTURE TO VALIDATE

```
User action → session.save() → IndexedDB → sync_queue → flush() → Supabase
                                                ↑
                              triggers: visibilitychange | online | 10min interval
```

Recovery Code flow:
```
Profile → copy XXXX-XXXX-XXXX → new device → enter code → restore() → pull from Supabase
```

