### BLOCK 3 — Offline Behavior (iOS Safari Critical)

3.1 Go offline before Save
    ACTION: disable network → complete workout → tap Save
    EXPECT: workout saved to IndexedDB ✓
    EXPECT: item added to sync_queue ✓
    EXPECT: Dynamic Island dot = pink/rose (#f472b6), gentle pulse animation
    EXPECT: Profile sync status = 'Offline'
    EXPECT: NO crash, NO error modal

3.2 Come back online
    ACTION: re-enable network
    EXPECT: `online` event fires → flush() triggered automatically
    EXPECT: sync_queue drained → Supabase row created
    EXPECT: island dot returns to green
    EXPECT: Profile sync status = 'Synced'

3.3 visibilitychange trigger (iOS Safari specific)
    ACTION: switch to another app → return to Fit Elite
    EXPECT: visibilitychange fires with state = 'visible'
    EXPECT: flush() called
    EXPECT: no duplicate records in Supabase (idempotent UPSERT by id)

3.4 Multiple offline sessions queue correctly
    ACTION: go offline → complete 3 workouts → save each → come online
    EXPECT: sync_queue contains 3 items
    EXPECT: all 3 upserted to Supabase in single batch flush
    EXPECT: sync_queue empty after flush

