### BLOCK 4 — Exponential Backoff

4.1 Simulate Supabase failure (rate limit / 5xx)
    ACTION: mock Supabase to return 503 on first 3 requests
    EXPECT: retry after 500ms → 1000ms → 2000ms
    EXPECT: max retry delay capped at 30000ms
    EXPECT: sync_queue item NOT removed on failed attempt
    EXPECT: status = 'pending' during retries
    EXPECT: success on 4th attempt → item removed → status = 'synced'

4.2 Network drops mid-flush
    ACTION: disconnect network during flush()
    EXPECT: _flushing flag resets to false
    EXPECT: no items removed from sync_queue
    EXPECT: retry scheduled after reconnect

